CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 20, 1959, pg. A3 reads: "Runners-up - E. Carter, left, presents second-place trophy to R. Robinson, second from left, while Odile Posey Bennett, second from right, receives the third-place trophy from R.L. Herrod, far right. The awards were won for highest production during National Insurance Week. North Carolina Mutual Life Insurance Company agents won all of the top prizes.-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: North Carolina Mutual Life Insurance Company winning agents, from left: R. Robinson, receiving second-place trophy from E. Carter, and Odile Posey Bennett, receiving third-place trophy from R.L. Herrod, posed in front of toteboard in interior
